	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="#regest1">
				<ab>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Gratia et pax, observande et charissime Bullingere.</s>
				</ab>
				<ab>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dici non potest, ut exhilararint nos literae tuae<note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2">Oben <ref target="files.xml#10786">Nr. 748</ref> (und 753?).</note>.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Pergite hac via; domini est, ne dubitetis.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nos <persName ref="138">Luthero</persName> omnia<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3"><persName ref="28">Bucer</persName> und <persName ref="40">Capito</persName> sandten unmittelbar nach ihrer Rückkehr vom Basler Konvent einen Bericht über die erzielte Einigung an <persName ref="138">Luther</persName>; s. WA Briefwechsel VII 357-359, <ref target="files.xml#12340">Nr. 2293</ref>; vgl. <hi>Köhler,</hi> ZL II 416f.</note>, sed propter itineris longitudinem nondum potuimus recipere responsum<note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4"><persName ref="138">Luther</persName> antwortete wegen Krankheit erst am 25. März. <persName ref="28">Bucer</persName> erhielt den Brief (WA Briefwechsel VII 378f, <ref target="files.xml#13050">Nr. 3001</ref>) am 11. April in <placeName ref="70">Augsburg</placeName>.</note>.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vulgus utrinque non semper sapit.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed verum est illos plus insanire, nec enim dum cum vulgo actum, quia cum ducibus nondum transactum est.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sustineamus opus domini.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Spero, quod tantopere expetis, te brevi habiturum<note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5">Bullinger hoffte auf ein freundliches Schreiben aus <placeName ref="1205">Wittenberg</placeName>; vgl. oben <ref target="files.xml#10786">Nr. 748</ref>, 12f. 16f; 753, 19f.</note>.</s>
				</ab>
				<ab>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="40">Capito</persName>, puto, pridem de filio d. doctoris medici scripsit<note xml:id="fn6" type="footnote" n="6">Siehe oben <ref target="files.xml#10800">Nr. 762</ref>, 1-11.</note>.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Habet quendam pharmacopolam<note xml:id="fn7" type="footnote" n="7">Unbekannt.</note>, qui illum recipere velit, sed pacisci, cum vident.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Alius quidam<pb type="edition" next="166"/><note xml:id="fn8" type="footnote" n="8">Unbekannt.</note> hac arte potentior recipiet eum, sed ad septembrem, et hic plus a pietate est; alter, ni fallor, vita nondum probavit se valde intelligere Christum.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">At religio primum in omni vita.</s>
				</ab>
				<ab>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Saluta plurimum totum illic sanctorum chorum, Leonem<note xml:id="fn9" type="footnote" n="9"><persName ref="114">Leo Jud</persName>.</note>, <persName ref="165">Pellicanum</persName>, <persName ref="14">Bibliandrum</persName> et reliquos.</s>
				</ab>
				<ab>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Arg[entorati], 11. marcii.</s>
				</ab>
				<ab>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">M. <persName ref="28">Bucerus</persName>.</s>
				</ab>
				<ab>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Eximio Christi servo M. Heylrycho Bullingero, symmystae et fratri suo observando.</s>
					<s xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tiguri.</s>
				</ab>
			</div>
